name: Agerin_Minosh
content:
Agerin Minosh was a Human male Mandalorian merchant who lived during the Galactic War. He resided on Corellia, where he built and sold armor in a small shop with the other vendors at the spaceport. He wore brown and silver Mandalorian armor.
Agerin Minosh appeared in the video game Star Wars: The Old Republic, released by BioWare in 2011, as an Equipment Commendations Vendor for Imperial players on Corellia. With the release of Game Update 4.0 on October 20, 2015, Minosh was removed from the game along with the rest of the Equipment Commendations Vendors.
